a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-2.7 1.814M2.748 7.447a.75.75 0 1 0-1.496.106l.5 7a.75.75 0 0 0 1.496-.106z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></span></button><button class="g-button g-button_view_flat-secondary g-button_size_m g-button_pin_round-round dc-control dc-feedback__control dc-feedback__control_view_regular dc-controls__control" aria-label="Not helpful" tabindex="0" type="button"><span class="g-button__icon"><span class="g-button__icon-inner"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="m12 9-2.94 5.041a1.932 1.932 0 0 1-3.56-1.378l.25-1.163.321-1.5h-2.94a2 2 0 0 1-1.927-2.535l.879-3.162A4 4 0 0 1 6.404 1.4L11.5 2zM6.229 2.89l3.863.455.379 5.3-2.708 4.64a.432.432 0 0 1-.796-.308l.571-2.663.389-1.814H3.13a.5.5 0 0 1-.482-.634l.879-3.162a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 2.7-1.814m7.023 5.663a.75.75 0 1 0 1.496-.106l-.5-7a.75.75 0 0 0-1.496.106z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></span></button></div></div><div class="dc-doc-page__main"><main class="dc-doc-page__content"><h1 class="dc-doc-page-title dc-doc-page__title"><span>Public IP address ranges in Yandex Cloud</span></h1><div class="dc-doc-page__under-title-info"><div class="dc-doc-page__page-contributors"><div class="dc-contributors"><div class="dc-contributors__title">Written by</div><div class="dc-contributor-avatars__one_contributor dc-contributor-avatars__one_contributor_onlyAuthor"><a href="/ru-kz" class="g-link g-link_view_normal"><img class="dc-contributor-avatars__avatar dc-contributor-avatars__avatar_size_small" src="https://storage.yandexcloud.net/cloud-www-assets/main-icons/docs/yc_team.svg"/></a><div><a href="/ru-kz" class="g-link g-link_view_normal">Yandex Cloud</a></div></div></div><div class="dc-updated-at-date"><div class="dc-updated-at-date__wrapper">Updated at<!-- --> <!-- -->June 26, 2026</div></div></div><div class="dc-doc-page__markdown-button"><a href="https://docs.yandex.cloud/int/en/security/ip-list.md" target="_blank" class="g-button g-button_view_normal g-button_size_m g-button_pin_round-round" tabindex="0" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-disabled="false"><span class="g-button__icon g-button__icon_side_start"><span class="g-button__icon-inner"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" width="16" height="16" class="g-icon" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.443 4.699A1.294 1.294 0 0 0 1 5.294v5.956a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0V6.139l1.834 3.54a.75.75 0 0 0 1.332 0L7.5 6.138v5.111a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0V5.294A1.294 1.294 0 0 0 6.557 4.7L5 7.703zm9.807.051a.75.75 0 0 0-1.5 0v4.69l-.47-.47a.75.75 0 1 0-1.06 1.06l1.75 1.75a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06 0l1.75-1.75a.75.75 0 1 0-1.06-1.06l-.47.47z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></svg></span></span><span class="g-button__text"> <!-- -->View in Markdown</span></a></div></div><div class="dc-doc-page__content-mini-toc yfm"><ul><li><a href="#yandex-resource-ips">IP addresses of Yandex Cloud resources available to customers</a><ul><li><a href="#virtual-private-cloud">Virtual Private Cloud</a></li><li><a href="#baremetal">BareMetal</a></li><li><a href="#cloud-cdn">Cloud CDN</a></li><li><a href="#smartcaptcha-ips">SmartCaptcha</a></li><li><a href="#sws-ips">Smart Web Security</a></li><li><a href="#security-deck-ips">Security Deck</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#yandex-cloud-ips">IP addresses used by Yandex Cloud for its services</a></li></ul></div><div class="dc-doc-page__body dc-doc-page__body_text-size_m yfm"><p>For Yandex Cloud network resources, two types of public IP addresses are used:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="ip-list#yandex-resource-ips">Yandex Cloud resource IP addresses</a> available to the customers, e.g., IP addresses of Compute Cloud VMs and database hosts.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="ip-list#yandex-cloud-ips">IP addresses used by Yandex Cloud to enable its services</a>, e.g., to record <a href="../audit-trails/concepts/format">audit logs</a> in Audit Trails.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="yandex-resource-ips"><a href="#yandex-resource-ips" class="yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor" aria-hidden="true"><span class="visually-hidden" data-no-index="true">IP addresses of Yandex Cloud resources available to customers</span></a>IP addresses of Yandex Cloud resources available to customers</h2>
