<p>For example, the resources assigned such IP address ranges are:</p>
<ul>
<li>Compute Cloud VMs</li>
<li>DB hosts</li>
<li>NAT instances</li>
<li>Network Load Balancer and Application Load Balancer load balancers</li>
</ul>
