<h3 id="cloud-cdn"><a href="#cloud-cdn" class="yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor" aria-hidden="true"><span class="visually-hidden" data-no-index="true">Cloud CDN</span></a>Cloud CDN</h3>
<p><a href="https://tech.cdn.yandex.net/prefixes/yc.json" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="yfm-external-link">List of public Yandex Cloud CDN IP addresses <span aria-label="External website. Opens in a new window" class="yfm-external-link__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 1.5A.75.75 0 0 0 10 3h1.94L6.97 7.97a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06 1.06L13 4.06V6a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0V2.25a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75zM7.5 3.25a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75H4.5a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v6a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h6a3 3 0 0 0 3-3V9.25a.75.75 0 0 0-1.5 0v2.25a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-6A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 11.5v-6A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 4h2.25a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg></span></a></p>
<h3 id="smartcaptcha-ips"><a href="#smartcaptcha-ips" class="yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor" aria-hidden="true"><span class="visually-hidden" data-no-index="true">SmartCaptcha</span></a>SmartCaptcha</h3>
<p>For SmartCaptcha to run correctly, enable access to the following IPs:</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>IPv4</th>
<th>IPv6</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-yc6nmtm0">84.201.151.229</code></td>
<td><code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-hthyjovs">2a0d:d6c1::1a:0:0:0:20e</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>They serve to ensure an API request sent to <code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-awr5nlsy">/validate</code> runs correctly.</p>
<p>These IP addresses cannot be assigned to user resources. They serve to ensure an API request sent to <code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-diwvedwf">/validate</code> works correctly.</p>
<h3 id="sws-ips"><a href="#sws-ips" class="yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor" aria-hidden="true"><span class="visually-hidden" data-no-index="true">Smart Web Security</span></a>Smart Web Security</h3>
<p>For Smart Web Security to run correctly, enable access to the following IPs:</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>IPv4</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-tjoxfg8q">46.243.212.0/24</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-dthkyeod">194.247.51.0/24</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>Access to these addresses is required for traffic to flow from the SWS <a href="../smartwebsecurity/concepts/domain-protect#proxy">proxy server</a> to target resources.</p>
<h3 id="security-deck-ips"><a href="#security-deck-ips" class="yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor" aria-hidden="true"><span class="visually-hidden" data-no-index="true">Security Deck</span></a>Security Deck</h3>
<h4 id="dspm"><a href="#dspm" class="yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor" aria-hidden="true"><span class="visually-hidden" data-no-index="true">DSPM</span></a>DSPM</h4>
<p>For the DSPM module to function correctly when controlling Object Storage bucket access using <a href="../storage/security/policy#conditional-writes-policy">policies</a>, you must allow access to the specified IP addresses in the policy settings:</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>IPv6</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-3u2hybxz">2a02:6b8:c0e:500:0:f898::/112</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-748mm0zj">2a02:6b8:c02:900:0:f898::/112</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-fl5viuoh">2a02:6b8:c41:1300:0:f898::/112</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2 id="yandex-cloud-ips"><a href="#yandex-cloud-ips" class="yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor" aria-hidden="true"><span class="visually-hidden" data-no-index="true">IP addresses used by Yandex Cloud for its services</span></a>IP addresses used by Yandex Cloud for its services</h2>
<p>The following IP address ranges are assigned to the resources that support Yandex Cloud operation:</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>IPv6</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-ecdygpgt">2a02:6b8::/32</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code class="yfm-clipboard-inline-code" role="button" aria-label="Code block" aria-description="To copy the text inside the block, click on the block" tabindex='0' id="inline-code-id-2pndyimm">2a0d:d6c0::/29</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>These IP address ranges are not available to users.</p>
<h4 id="see-also"><a href="#see-also" class="yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor" aria-hidden="true"><span class="visually-hidden" data-no-index="true">See also</span></a>See also</h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="../smartcaptcha/concepts/ips">SmartCaptcha public IP addresses</a></li>
<li><a href="https://yandex.com/ips" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="yfm-external-link">IP address ranges used by Yandex<span aria-label="External website. Opens in a new window" class="yfm-external-link__icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 1.5A.75.75 0 0 0 10 3h1.94L6.97 7.97a.75.75 0 0 0 1.06 1.06L13 4.06V6a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0V2.25a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75zM7.5 3.25a.75.75 0 0 0-.75-.75H4.5a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v6a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h6a3 3 0 0 0 3-3V9.25a.75.75 0 0 0-1.5 0v2.25a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5h-6A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 3 11.5v-6A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 4.5 4h2.25a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg></span></a></li>
</ul>
