__DATA__ = {"err":null,"props":{"pageProps":{"data":{"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Public IP address ranges","url":"/en/docs/security/ip-list"}],"html":"\u003cp\u003eFor Yandex Cloud network resources, two types of public IP addresses are used:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"ip-list#yandex-resource-ips\"\u003eYandex Cloud resource IP addresses\u003c/a\u003e available to the customers, e.g., IP addresses of Compute Cloud VMs and database hosts.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"ip-list#yandex-cloud-ips\"\u003eIP addresses used by Yandex Cloud to enable its services\u003c/a\u003e, e.g., to record \u003ca href=\"../audit-trails/concepts/format\"\u003eaudit logs\u003c/a\u003e in Audit Trails.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"yandex-resource-ips\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"#yandex-resource-ips\" class=\"yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visually-hidden\" data-no-index=\"true\"\u003eIP addresses of Yandex Cloud resources available to customers\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003eIP addresses of Yandex Cloud resources available to customers\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"virtual-private-cloud\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"#virtual-private-cloud\" class=\"yfm-anchor yfm-clipboard-anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visually-hidden\" data-no-index=\"true\"\u003eVirtual Private Cloud\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003eVirtual Private Cloud\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003ctable\u003e\n\u003cthead\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eIPv4\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/thead\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\u003ccode class=\"yfm-clipboard-inline-code\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Code block\" aria-description=\"To copy the text inside the block, click on the block\" tabindex='0' id=\"inline-code-id-zgbyy10f\"\u003e31.44.8.0/21\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e\u00